  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX spot at 6776.8 sitting just above the GEX flip at 6774, dealers are in positive gamma territory and likely selling delta into strength here as price approaches the massive 6785 wall (33.9B GEX). The PIN regime with heavy positive gamma concentration between 6775-6800 creates a strong magnet effect, with dealers providing natural resistance on any push toward 6785-6800 and support on dips toward 6765 negative gamma. Key levels to watch are the 6774 flip line as the regime pivot and 6785 as the primary resistance where dealer selling pressure intensifies.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect price to get pinned between 6765-6785 with choppy mean-reverting action.",
